    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>  
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle St: Camden</name>
                    <date when="1885-11-09" rend="right">Nov: 9 '85<ptr target="tex.00448_n1"
                        /></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear T D</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Yours rec'd with L[awrence] B[arrett]'s check &#38; the ferry pass<ptr
                    target="tex.00448_n2"/>&#8212;Many &#38; best thanks&#8212;I will come over
                &#38; see you all soon.</p>
            <p>I am in good spirits, &#38; somewhat better, but fearfully lame &#38; disabled
                    yet<ptr target="tex.00448_n3"/>&#8212;go out with the horse &#38; buggy every
                    afternoon<ptr target="tex.00448_n4"/>&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>W W</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
